         <p class="- topic/p ">Remove the gland plates and drill
the required holes for the cables connecting to the terminals in the
system.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The cable entry for the system can either be from the
bottom, the top or both.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Drill the holes in the gland plates
so that the connecting cables can be as straight as possible when
attached to the terminals.</p>
